resolution: Recorded the accepted ADR for the profile lint severity model in the item body (Context/Decision/Consequences) reflecting the implementation shipped in PR #404.
expected_result: "A durable decision record explaining why lintProjectProfile grades findings as errors (apply-breaking / data-loss) versus warnings (structurally-valid suspicious cross-references), and how assertProjectProfile gates them."
actual_result: "ADR body added and accepted; the model is implemented in src/core/profile/profile-lint.ts and enforced by assertProjectProfile (throws on errors; strict also on warnings), covered at 100% in #404."
